to go back to Lake Geneva, for TSR was near to being placed into involuntary bankruptcy. In subsequent months I lost the suit for control of TSR. No meaningful entity in the motion picture business, or TV entertainment, would deal with TSR, so that deal an
d one for a spinoff of the cartoon show were flushed. Mr. Wells died. }}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f1\fs24\lang1033\i0\b0{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "http://piedpiperpublishing.yuku.com/topic/2281" }{\fldrslt \*\cs8\cf2\ul\ulc0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f1\fs24\lang1033\loch\f1\fs24\lang1033{\cf1\ul\ulc0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f3\fs20\lang1025\loch\f3\fs20\lang1025 [EGG] http://piedpiperpublishing.yuku.com/topic/2281}}}}
