n a ledge was then assailed and laid low--many a Magic Missile lightening the combat load on the other characters in the melee. }}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f1\fs24\lang1033\i0\b0{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "http://www.enworld.org/forums/showthread.php?t=22566&page=2&pp=30" }{\fldrslt \*\cs8\cf2\ul\ulc0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f1\fs24\lang1033\loch\f1\fs24\lang1033{\cf1\ul\ulc0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f3\fs20\lang1025\loch\f3\fs20\lang1025 [EGG] http://www.enworld.org/forums/showthread.php?t=22566&page=2&pp=30}}}}
