ame the most potent weapon in that group's arsenal! }}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f1\fs24\lang1033\i0\b0{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "http://www.enworld.org/forums/showthread.php?t=46861&page=9&pp=15" }{\fldrslt \*\cs8\cf2\ul\ulc0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f1\fs24\lang1033\loch\f1\fs24\lang1033{\cf1\ul\ulc0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f3\fs20\lang1025\loch\f3\fs20\lang1025 [EGG] http://www.enworld.org/forums/showthread.php?t=46861&page=9&pp=15}}}}
