\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af1\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af1\langfe255\hich\f1\fs24\lang1033\loch\f1\fs24\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f1\fs24\lang1033\i0\b0{\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f3\fs20\lang1025\loch\f3\fs20\lang1025 The whole of the combined material Rob and I put together would be far too large for publication, 50 levels or so. What I have done is gone back to my original design of more modest scope, because I doubt the work will need to accommodate groups of 20 PCs 
delving on a daily basis.\line \line As Rob learned from me, he too DMed by the proverbial seat of the pants method. A single line of notes for an encounter was sufficient for wither of us to detail a lengthy description, action, dialog, tricks or traps, and all the
 rest. As this is not the stuff of modules, we will have to do the same thing as we go over each encounter on the map, actually recording our otherwise extemporized details for the reader.\line \line The most interesting and demanding features of levels will be reta
ined, but the maps will have to be re-drawn from originals. the latter were altered as we merged dungeons, and as PCs interacted with the complex. At one time Robilar, Tenser, and Terik converted the first level of the dungeons to their base.\line \line In short the
 original upper and lower parts of Castle Greyhawk changed many times over the years they were in active use. What we will do is to take the best of the lot and put that into a detailed format usable by anyone, no "winging-it' required. Noite that it is "Z
agyg's Castle", so no tedious explanations of how the denizens of the place got there will be needed. }}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f1\fs24\lang1033\i0\b0{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "http://www.enworld.org/forums/showthread.php?t=57832&page=12&pp=15" }{\fldrslt \*\cs8\cf2\ul\ulc0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f1\fs24\lang1033\loch\f1\fs24\lang1033{\cf1\ul\ulc0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f3\fs20\lang1025\loch\f3\fs20\lang1025 [EGG] http://www.enworld.org/forums/showthread.php?t=57832&page=12&pp=15}}}}
