nformation was originally presented in The Rogues Gallery and Mordenkainen's Fantastic Adventure.\line \line The Circle of Eight\line The characters that make up The Circle of Eight are all PCs of Gary Gygax. Some were made from scratch as PCs, some were created to serve
 as recruited henchmen, and a few were encountered NPCs that ended up as permanent additions to the circle. The members of the circle roam the far reaches of the Flanaess and beyond. Several members have magical means of traveling , but others do all their
